Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.97,0:00:06.16,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,You mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.09,0:00:08.98,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.71,0:00:14.41,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure I'll grant your wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.68,0:00:21.79,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Nonoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.19,0:00:24.24,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.49,0:00:26.75,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,was together.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.94,0:00:30.34,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Yuzuki. Koharu. Mizusaka-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.10,0:00:32.26,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,And Togawa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.29,0:00:34.41,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Nonoka...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.95,0:00:36.76,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.01,0:00:44.66,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Look, Nonoka, everyone's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.66,0:00:45.94,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,That means...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.05,0:00:51.13,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,We're all here! We're all here! \NWe're all here!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.58,0:00:54.95,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I need to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.32,0:00:58.17,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,We should go back down the \Nmountain before it gets dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.17,0:00:59.50,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.66,0:01:02.00,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Let's meet up with the teachers first.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.00,0:01:02.95,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Nonoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.95,0:01:04.24,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.83,0:01:05.83,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I'd forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.69,0:01:12.13,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,About the observatory, and about \Nthe time we all played together.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.76,0:01:14.80,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,And that I couldn't say goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.59,0:01:17.68,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,And that we called the saucer.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.80,0:01:28.82,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Yuzuki, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.96,0:01:30.06,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Koharu.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.49,0:01:32.56,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.81,0:01:41.92,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.69,0:01:45.19,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,So what if you'd forgotten?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.58,0:01:47.65,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,You thought we'd forgive \Nyou because of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.65,0:02:00.66,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.44,0:03:37.23,sora-ep-title,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(730,430)}A Fragment of Emotions
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.01,0:03:54.96,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Sparkle!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.29,0:04:01.47,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.97,0:04:44.01,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Noel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.81,0:04:45.34,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Noel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.13,0:04:47.28,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Nonoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.57,0:04:52.06,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.38,0:04:53.98,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.43,0:04:58.90,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,I thought your wishes would come \Ntrue if we all came together.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.90,0:05:00.48,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,But it wasn't like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.44,0:05:04.46,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,I was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.61,0:05:06.72,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,So, sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.22,0:05:10.65,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, my wishes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.79,0:05:13.04,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.26,0:05:14.25,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.48,0:05:17.17,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,So cheer up, Nonoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.64,0:05:19.70,sora-main,Shuichi,0000,0000,0000,,Nonoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.54,0:05:22.88,sora-main,Shuichi,0000,0000,0000,,Do we have a guest?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.37,0:05:24.44,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.44,0:05:26.38,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Don't come out dressed like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.02,0:05:29.92,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.74,0:05:34.39,sora-main,Shuichi,0000,0000,0000,,I did a good job cracking \Nthe eggs today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.23,0:05:38.40,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,She'll try hard, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.40,0:05:41.13,sora-main,Shuichi,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be a shame if my cooking gets col—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.13,0:05:43.23,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I have to go out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.22,0:05:45.23,sora-main,Shuichi,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.94,0:06:12.01,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Noel, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.03,0:06:17.33,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.49,0:06:18.98,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,It's so early.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.39,0:06:21.48,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,I want to talk about something.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.87,0:06:25.09,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.93,0:06:28.78,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.01,0:06:32.26,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, is it about Nonoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.33,0:06:35.99,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Then I don't intend to forgive \Nher or apologize to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.62,0:06:37.82,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,She deserved it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.82,0:06:41.25,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,No, I want to talk about \NNonoka, too, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.64,0:06:42.83,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.73,0:06:46.13,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Did you call her?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.40,0:06:49.32,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.49,0:06:50.47,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.30,0:06:52.73,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.86,0:06:55.01,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,You tricked us, and then disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.63,0:06:58.54,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Do you even know what happened \Nbecause of the saucer?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.06,0:07:04.21,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.73,0:07:09.40,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I want to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.27,0:07:11.77,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me about this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.59,0:07:14.92,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Please, Yuzuki, tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.06,0:07:18.36,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,How could I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.83,0:07:26.55,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to tell you anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.02,0:07:30.55,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,I have things I need to be doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.93,0:07:34.36,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to keep doing that thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.05,0:07:36.05,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.83,0:07:38.81,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to drive the saucer away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.98,0:07:40.06,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.09,0:07:43.06,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Yuzuki, listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.34,0:07:44.94,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Just leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.74,0:07:48.97,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,The saucer, Nonoka, Koharu, Souta...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.12,0:07:50.53,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,I hate you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.94,0:07:52.22,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Yuzuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.19,0:07:59.45,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,I guess
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.91,0:08:02.42,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.19,0:08:11.18,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Koharu, what's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.35,0:08:14.09,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Souta, where are you right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.99,0:08:16.85,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm heading home from school.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.85,0:08:18.05,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.05,0:08:22.53,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to talk to you about \NYuzuki if you were nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.61,0:08:26.09,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.22,0:08:27.27,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,No, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.74,0:08:30.74,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,I just couldn't explain properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.08,0:08:34.18,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry too much about Yuzuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.02,0:08:36.25,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,The bus is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.25,0:08:37.28,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.10,0:08:41.62,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.26,0:08:45.17,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, so rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.83,0:08:54.51,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,It's the saucer's fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.63,0:09:10.96,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Mizusaka-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.07,0:09:15.68,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.00,0:09:18.53,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Please help!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.53,0:09:23.54,Saucer,Text,0000,0000,0000,,No Saucer
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.99,0:09:23.54,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Please help us drive \Nthe saucer out of town!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.54,0:09:25.74,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Please, help us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.51,0:09:28.04,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.04,0:09:29.71,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,At least take this, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.89,0:09:31.02,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.02,0:09:32.66,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,The details are...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.55,0:09:38.18,Saucer2,Text,0000,0000,0000,,No saucer!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.95,0:09:46.33,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Please help!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.69,0:09:49.65,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Please hear me out, just a little!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.90,0:09:53.15,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.15,0:09:54.95,sora-flashback,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.40,0:09:57.28,sora-flashback,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,No saucer!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.55,0:10:00.41,sora-flashback,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Please help!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.90,0:10:04.04,sora-flashback,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Let's drive the saucer out of town!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.58,0:10:06.46,sora-flashback,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Let's drive the—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.16,0:10:12.61,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.07,0:10:20.12,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.39,0:10:23.32,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Please help!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.31,0:10:25.44,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Noel.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.74,0:10:27.41,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,We promised.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.00,0:10:32.26,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.02,0:10:35.78,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Hip hip hooray!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.03,0:10:37.99,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.35,0:10:40.52,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Please help!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.17,0:10:52.42,Juice,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Dew of Kiriyako
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.36,0:10:52.42,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.57,0:10:54.59,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.84,0:10:56.88,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,My sister's causing you trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.73,0:10:59.88,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,It's my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.05,0:11:04.89,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Mizusaka-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.49,0:11:12.73,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Were you at school?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.86,0:11:15.88,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,About my career options.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.28,0:11:18.24,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,There isn't anyone else \Ngoing to study abroad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.28,0:11:21.24,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I can only talk to the \Nteachers about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.56,0:11:22.76,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,You're studying abroad?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.70,0:11:25.01,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Just so you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.30,0:11:28.45,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,it has nothing to do with the fact \Nthat I don't get along with Yuzuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.46,0:11:30.25,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I-I wouldn't have...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.93,0:11:34.75,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I've always planned to go \Noverseas after middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.96,0:11:38.76,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.86,0:11:42.07,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,You were fighting over steamed buns.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.21,0:11:43.76,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,That was a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.49,0:11:51.33,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,But she's really doing all \Nthat to get back at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.94,0:11:54.77,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,It might be good for us to \Nbe away from each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.84,0:11:59.20,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,To get back at you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.09,0:12:03.93,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,She probably wants to bother \Nme because she hates me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.50,0:12:07.66,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.66,0:12:15.06,sora-flashback,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,There are still some things that \Nhaven't gone back to how they were.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.49,0:12:20.66,sora-flashback,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,They used to launch \Nfireworks from the lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.86,0:12:22.93,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Fireworks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.59,0:12:28.14,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Yuzuki still wants \Nto see the fireworks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.76,0:12:31.06,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Fireworks?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.23,0:12:32.64,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Obviously we can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.82,0:12:36.40,sora-flashback,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.82,0:12:39.97,sora-flashback,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,We promised to watch \Nthe fireworks together!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.13,0:12:42.48,sora-flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,They were canceled \Nbecause of the saucer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.48,0:12:44.03,sora-flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want me to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.80,0:12:50.09,sora-flashback,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.64,0:12:54.99,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid Yuzuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.42,0:12:59.42,shop,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Shiihara Shop
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.89,0:12:59.42,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.99,0:13:02.06,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Please help!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.23,0:13:04.93,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look at the saucer!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.38,0:13:06.62,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.78,0:13:08.86,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look at the saucer!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.03,0:13:09.89,sora-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.86,0:13:13.48,sora-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Because it's embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.97,0:13:16.93,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.08,0:13:20.07,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,It's because nothing good comes \Nof being involved with the saucer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.34,0:13:22.99,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Noel, don't \Nsay weird things.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.19,0:13:25.18,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,But!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.49,0:13:28.13,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.83,0:13:39.33,Palace,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Saucer Palace
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.09,0:13:49.96,sora-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.30,0:13:51.28,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.20,0:13:53.81,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.95,0:13:56.83,sora-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's that outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.82,0:13:59.60,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.93,0:14:01.23,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.46,0:14:05.00,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Please help!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.13,0:14:06.29,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Yuzuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.12,0:14:08.12,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.84,0:14:10.57,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Can I ask you to stop?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.81,0:14:14.20,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,It's bothering the customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.05,0:14:16.75,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not bothering them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.75,0:14:18.91,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm getting complaints from customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.25,0:14:23.19,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,You're saying that to try to \Nget rid of me, too, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.19,0:14:24.25,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Like the other places.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.61,0:14:27.95,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Please, Yuzuki, don't make me say any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.01,0:14:30.37,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.79,0:14:34.26,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for the trouble, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.29,0:14:39.44,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.62,0:14:40.83,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.46,0:14:45.94,sora-flashback,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.28,0:14:47.98,sora-flashback,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Um, here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.81,0:14:52.19,sora-flashback,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,I'll help.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.83,0:14:56.68,sora-flashback,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,But are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.68,0:14:57.48,sora-flashback,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.60,0:15:00.33,sora-flashback,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm always on your side, Yuzuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.10,0:15:04.09,sora-internal,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.19,0:15:15.18,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Yuzuki,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.14,0:15:18.16,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,where are we going next?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.68,0:15:22.28,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,There's nowhere left to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.98,0:15:26.75,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,I'll work even harder.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.39,0:15:28.38,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.98,0:15:31.32,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,It's not worth it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.80,0:15:33.79,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for helping me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.79,0:15:34.71,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.66,0:15:37.62,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.65,0:16:00.03,sora-main,C,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with that kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.14,0:16:05.06,sora-flashback,A,0000,0000,0000,,What is that Mizusaka-san person doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.31,0:16:06.36,sora-flashback,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.36,0:16:08.38,sora-flashback,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,We live in different towns,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.38,0:16:10.72,sora-flashback,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,but if this whole class cooperates,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.62,0:16:14.70,sora-flashback,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,I think we can get rid of the saucer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.70,0:16:15.92,sora-flashback,B,0000,0000,0000,,What's with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.92,0:16:18.23,sora-flashback,A,0000,0000,0000,,Mizusaka hasn't changed, \Neven in middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.23,0:16:19.70,sora-flashback,C,0000,0000,0000,,If only she didn't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.04,0:16:21.71,sora-flashback,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, listen up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.08,0:16:25.30,sora-flashback,D,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't you think so, too, Shiihara-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.07,0:16:29.70,sora-flashback,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,I know Yuzuki really well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.85,0:16:31.19,sora-flashback,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,So I can't laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.41,0:16:34.22,sora-flashback,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know her. How can \Nyou say something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.76,0:16:37.22,sora-flashback,A,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.12,0:16:52.65,sora-flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Could you stop helping Yuzuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.15,0:16:54.03,sora-flashback,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.40,0:16:58.78,sora-flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want her to cause you trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.16,0:17:00.79,sora-flashback,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.23,0:17:08.88,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad we talked.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.39,0:17:10.72,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.84,0:17:15.78,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, Koharu probably understands \NYuzuki better than I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.05,0:17:18.45,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.81,0:17:23.89,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you make up with Yuzuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.18,0:17:29.40,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.77,0:17:32.26,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I used to know everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.52,0:17:36.40,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,How can I help her?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.45,0:17:40.40,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Can you talk to her, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.44,0:17:45.66,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I will, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.68,0:17:52.67,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Why won't anyone understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.30,0:17:57.54,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need anyone if \Nnobody's going to help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.31,0:18:06.46,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Yuzuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.51,0:18:08.31,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Yuzuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.00,0:18:10.74,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Yuzuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.12,0:18:13.44,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.68,0:18:14.57,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get in my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.17,0:18:16.83,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it already.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.97,0:18:19.98,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,You're just causing people trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.98,0:18:21.16,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,You're not accomplishing anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.51,0:18:24.58,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,You're more worried about \Nyour shop, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.47,0:18:31.67,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,How could you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.26,0:18:34.37,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,You're just like Souta.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.18,0:18:39.18,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,You think what I'm doing is stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.30,0:18:45.27,sora-flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,But you know that what Yuzuki's \Ndoing is pointless, right, Koharu?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.60,0:18:47.10,sora-flashback,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.21,0:18:51.91,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,You think it doesn't mean \Nanything, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.67,0:18:58.83,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,You do, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.99,0:19:01.36,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.81,0:19:03.42,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.33,0:19:11.88,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.94,0:19:25.39,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,I hate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.04,0:20:23.99,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,The one thing I can do...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.50,0:20:38.42,Closed,Text,0000,0000,0000,,We're closed for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.18,0:21:27.26,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Koharu!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.67,0:21:29.82,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Nonoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.37,0:21:31.66,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.84,0:21:36.23,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Did you need something?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.32,0:21:47.78,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Lend me a hand, Koharu.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.50,0:23:33.89,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode of {\i1}Celestial \NMethod{\i0}: "Flower of Light."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.17,0:23:35.56,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Enjoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.56,0:23:39.06,sora-next-ep,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Flower of Light
